{"tid":2046844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"292萬多人到街站簽名及到網上聯署支持国安法","createTime":"2020-06-01T16:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T18:02:47.000Z","uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7c9503f2ed7deaa12b90036c8ad9411654dfab","tid":2046844,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1296711&amp;category_id=341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshare.881903.com%2F%3Fnews_id%3D1296711%26category_id%3D341&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8x0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=fc51f373\" target=\"_blank\">https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1296711&amp;category_id=341</a><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任駱惠寧同香港各界&ldquo;撐國安立法&rdquo;代表座談交流時出，<span style=\"color: red;\">僅8天時間，就有292萬多人到街站簽名及到網上聯署</span>，說明就香港維護國家安全立法是人心所向、勢在必行。他說，社會上有人煽動說國安法出台後，市民沒有言論、出版、集會、遊行自由，甚至出國旅遊、和外國人吃飯都會被抓起來，是聳人聽聞，無非是要在社會製造無端恐懼，挑撥仇恨，希望市民與謠言背後的政治圖謀做堅決的切割，對一切外來干預，中央都將採取有力措施予以回擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200601/s00001/1590987586438/%e8%ad%9a%e8%80%80%e5%ae%97-%e3%80%8c%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%a8%e3%80%8d%e6%8a%8a%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%b8%b6%e5%8e%bb%e6%ad%bb%e8%b7%af-%e6%87%89%e9%81%bf%e5%85%8d%e5%8f%ab%e3%80%8c%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f%e4%b8%80%e9%bb%a8%e5%b0%88%e6%94%bf%e3%80%8d%e5%8f%a3%e8%99%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200601%2Fs00001%2F1590987586438%2F%25e8%25ad%259a%25e8%2580%2580%25e5%25ae%2597-%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25a8%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%258a%258a%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25b8%25b6%25e5%258e%25bb%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e8%25b7%25af-%25e6%2587%2589%25e9%2581%25bf%25e5%2585%258d%25e5%258f%25ab%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25b5%2590%25e6%259d%259f%25e4%25b8%2580%25e9%25bb%25a8%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%2594%25bf%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%258f%25a3%25e8%2599%259f&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8x0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=2753bd94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200601%2Fs00001%2F1590987586438%2F%25e8%25ad%259a%25e8%2580%2580%25e5%25ae%2597-%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25a8%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%258a%258a%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25b8%25b6%25e5%258e%25bb%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e8%25b7%25af-%25e6%2587%2589%25e9%2581%25bf%25e5%2585%258d%25e5%258f%25ab%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25b5%2590%25e6%259d%259f%25e4%25b8%2580%25e9%25bb%25a8%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%2594%25bf%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%258f%25a3%25e8%2599%259f&h=341383a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200601/s00001/1590987586438/%e8%ad%9a%e8%80%80%e5%ae%97-%e3%80%8c%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%a8%e3%80%8d%e6%8a%8a%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%b8%b6%e5%8e%bb%e6%ad%bb%e8%b7%af-%e6%87%89%e9%81%bf%e5%85%8d%e5%8f%ab%e3%80%8c%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f%e4%b8%80%e9%bb%a8%e5%b0%88%e6%94%bf%e3%80%8d%e5%8f%a3%e8%99%9f</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗今早（6月1日）接受商台節目訪問時，提及「港獨」議題，稱香港是中國領土，希望行回「一國兩制」的正軌，<span style=\"color: red;\">提倡「港獨」是想把香港變成「一國一制」</span>，這沒有出路、把香港帶去死路。他說，有些人<span style=\"color: red;\">以為有外國勢力撐腰是「嘥氣」</span>，他們只是被利用，又說自己常常苦口婆心勸喻別人懸崖勒馬，「唔好搞喇」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529496-20200601.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529496-20200601.htm&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8x0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=8e133748\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529496-20200601.htm&h=775e98e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529496-20200601.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠又說，市民可以出席合法遊行、集會，但如果有人改變活動性質，例如出現暴力事件，或者有人叫「結束一黨專政」口號，她會呼籲市民離開，形容「君子不立危牆之下」。<span style=\"color: red;\">她又認為，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國不是「一黨專政」</span></span>，而是一黨領導、多黨合作，這個口號是「偽議題」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529625-20200601.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529625-20200601.htm&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8x0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=5388afb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529625-20200601.htm&h=ada7b6fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529625-20200601.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n8間教資會資助的大學校董會主席發表聯合聲明，表示作為香港市民，得到國家給予的保障，同時有責任保護國家安全，除了支持基本法，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦支持建立健全特區維護國家安全的法律制度與執行機制，藉以防止危害國家安全的行為及活動，國家安全法有利維護香港繁榮穩定，有利香港「一國兩制」行穩致遠</span>，有利為大學教育與科研提供安寧環境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當我地諗緊點樣介入美國示威<br />\n點樣比較美國示威同香港示威<br />\n點樣搵中共滲透美國示威嘅證據<br />\n睇下班保皇點樣積極搞9香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">國際戰線<br />\n議會<br />\n街頭抗爭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ade427b129748653b6887c082eaf31857f308f2","tid":2046844,"uid":13029,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"姐係有500萬人反對"},{"pid":"e3805fabcb60c459adbbb7948b479226e4a4565c","tid":2046844,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ade427b129748653b6887c082eaf31857f308f2","tid":2046844,"uid":13029,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"姐係有500萬人反對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1c97c64aa5bfc6e7a2b8e6901817d6f1c50408","tid":2046844,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"公開名單生生世世不得出國"},{"pid":"d91ecf4b49ccf0fd29bb129f0ae50e0ac6a6cf46","tid":2046844,"uid":73281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"即係有13億同胞反對"},{"pid":"7544389dbf0ba5f713f0ed57bb186dcf26aaff07","tid":2046844,"uid":75782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"誠信早已破產 你做乜都冇人信<br />\n<br />\n話夠一億吖"},{"pid":"903eb58bae8122e22ded665854bcaebdde6c7cff","tid":2046844,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"返送中夠話有好多人簽名支持"}]}